    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1942-04-23T07:35:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1942-04-23T07:35:00-05:00" n="391"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d391">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">701.9491/23: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Iran</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Dreyfus</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Tehran</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1942-04-23T16:00:00+03:25"
                            >April 23, 1942—4 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received 9:21 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>120. Referring to my 104,<note n="4" xml:id="d391fn4">Dated April 13, noon, <ref
                            target="#pg_333">p. 333</ref>.</note> the Japanese Legation left Tehran
                    this morning en route to Japan via Russia.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Dreyfus</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
